data.description: WELCOME TO SUN CITY- An active 55-plus gated community located in the Heart of Apple Valley . This Golf course community offers the finest Leisure style living in the High Desert. There is also a security guard located at the gate.  The floor plan is open with lots of natural light and large and updated and is ready for those large family gatherings. The Solar panels. Both bedrooms are large and located on opposite sides of the home for privacy. This a Turn-key stunning well kept home that you are looking for. Come and see.
